Subject: Codex Conversation Agent Spawn Node

Description: Spawn-node contract that attaches a root submission to a Codex app conversation, builds a bounded job frame, and coordinates LM Studio hosted Codex CLI agents through explicit launch, capture, and authority gates.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-25_codex_conversation_agent_spawn_node\Dictated_Codex_Conversation_Agent_Spawn_Node_Source.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\LLMAgentCollaborationFabric.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\CodexLMStudioOrchestrationWorkspace.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\LocalAIManagerPrimary.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SOPTaskManager.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\TaskFrameLaunchQueue.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SOPWorkerBootPacket.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SOPLanguagePrimerForLocalAgents.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SecurityHonestyGovernance.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\FrameReferenceIntegrity.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\LocalIdentityConsumption.sop
